{"1897000":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"Pow! 2","steam_appid":1897000,"required_age":0,"is_free":false,"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">POW! 2<\/h2><br>You must help Spike, the Blue Ball, and take him to the target platform with the help of your friends. Calculate the timers, configure the friends, hit play, and watch the action! <br><br>This is <strong>Spike<\/strong>, the guy who has the power to activate the <strong>target platform<\/strong>. Next to him, we have a famous <strong>target platform<\/strong>. When it enters in contact with Spike for 3 seconds, it has the power to transport everybody to another level.<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1897000\/extras\/player_target.gif?t=1646648880\" \/><br><br>Your goal is to take Spike there with the help of your friends. Reach the target in less than the expected time and you win an achievement!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Meet your friends<\/h2><br><strong>Red Larry<\/strong> is a nice and explosive guy! When it's time to act, he sends it all away!<br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1897000\/extras\/explosion.gif?t=1646648880\" \/><br><br>Here we have <strong>Ed Van Ish<\/strong> e <strong>Thomas Orange<\/strong>. Ed is always tired! When it is his time to shine, he simply disappears. Thomas, on the other hand, is a quiet guy. But don’t get it wrong! With his connections and knowledge, he can make other blocks act!<br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1897000\/extras\/vanish_trigger.gif?t=1646648880\" \/><br><br><strong>Lucy<\/strong> is always here to help! She can move things in any direction!<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\/apps\/1897000\/extras\/moving.gif?t=1646648880\" \/><br><br>And don't forget the <strong>Portals<\/strong>, they can transport <strong>Spike<\/strong> and other elements to other parts.<br><br><img src=\"https:\/\/cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com\/steam\